Joseph Rodney MCLAIN, Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
STATE of Florida, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D19-0532 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. March 26, 2019

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

Petitioner's petition for belated appeal is denied. See Jordan v. State, 549 So. 2d 805 , 806 (Fla. 1st DCA 1989).

MORRIS, BLACK, and ROTHSTEIN-YOUAKIM, JJ., Concur.
